{"tid":2296031,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"確診者獲5000元津貼　網民質疑港府鼓勵人除口罩博染疫","createTime":"2020-11-22T07:18:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T08:27:51.000Z","uid":66271,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a18658666b99fee5e7cda4f33a060844d9b45f8c","tid":2296031,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T07:18:20.000Z","msg":"第四波新冠肺炎殺入本港，港府早前宣布將為本地感染確診者提供津貼，尤其基層市民對強制檢測可能會卻步，故提供金額一筆過5000港元資助，但卻不設資產審查；措施一出隨即引起網民熱議，質疑港府的「智將」隨時令更多人除罩博中肺炎，更有網民笑指，誠徵確診者口水，稱「1000蚊一篤仲有錢賺」。<br />\n<br />\n疫情反彈，港府束手無策；今次宣布派發5000港元措施一出，網上討論區隨即瘋狂洗版，有網民抱不平，認為確診應該罰錢，但現時有獎金，便有如鼓勵人「中招」，批評措施本末倒置；亦有幽默的網民指，「又可以唔返工，又可以直接袋多5000蚊，好賺過賭錢」。<br />\n<br />\n此外，更有網民出謀獻策，留言誠徵確診者口水，亦有網民「心水清」，笑指「重複中100次，已經有50萬，一家4口每人中100次，就有200萬，上車可期」。"},{"pid":"0f3ef9afd9fc02784235f320615cb46f9dabcf6b","tid":2296031,"uid":137493,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T07:20:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3515e1b2abd5a75949f482890d83a91167764515","tid":2296031,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T07:22:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />發達大計<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />脫貧真係夠呢鋪啦"},{"pid":"a4e3f34bf7e3899468e474f3ecf673ad2aa60ebc","tid":2296031,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T07:23:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />發達大計<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />脫貧真係<span class=\"red\">靠</span>呢鋪啦</blockquote>"},{"pid":"896fe0ba833068696eb96766e1c7e8fc60c9540a","tid":2296031,"uid":304916,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a4e3f34bf7e3899468e474f3ecf673ad2aa60ebc","tid":2296031,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T07:23:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />發達大計<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />脫貧真係<span class=\"red\">靠</span>呢鋪啦</blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T07:35:35.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"b944f10e54867be32fdca2627082c79d2443e92e","tid":2296031,"uid":365791,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T07:37:41.000Z","msg":"我都唔想返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔洗做就有得袋5000<br />\n入去火神山住幾晚出黎又一條好漢，仲包食包住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4321bbd440f94d3af8b1904bb1f3319c1fd14a8","tid":2296031,"uid":164477,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T08:27:51.000Z","msg":"講真 拎開綜緩個班撚樣真係會駁中招"}]}